org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.xquery
Class AeNoOpVariable

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.ext.expr.def.xquery.AeNoOpVariable
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.sf.saxon.expr.Expression, java.io.Serializable
public class AeNoOpVariable
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.sf.saxon.expr.Expression

An implementation of an Expression that is used only for parsing for validation/analysis. This is an object that will exist in the parsed XQuery AST, but is not meant for execution.
